div.div:
NFR24L01 Pins
Pin 1 = GND
Pin 2 = VCC
Pin 3 = CE
Pin 4 = CSN
Pin 5 = SCK
Pin 6 = MOSI
Pin 7 = MISO
Pin 8 = IRQ
PA0 = 0 = RX
PA1 = 1 = TX
PA2 = 2 = CSN (any pin)
PA3 = 3 = CE (any pin)
PA4 = 4 = SCK
PA5 = 5 = MISO
PA6 = 6 = MOSI
Free
PA0 = 13
PA1 = 12
PA7 = 7 = Analog possible
PB2 = 8
PB3 = 11
PB1 = 9
PB0 = 10
VCC = pin 1
GND = pin 14
